n港獨支那趕中產， 冇和理非就含家產</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"打呢個副本，可以一有怪獸黎幫拖，就即刻轉去第二區繼續搞"},{"pid":"9d44db2694640c68ee9062570ad461b19810f0f1","tid":1383671,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:12:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e0455ec961ad02bc799a84ed529d3e53c58ac17a","tid":1383671,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:14:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"238d54a0943947905a47ba432b27f1c5655b98f9","tid":1383671,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:14:24.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />算了聽日再推"},{"pid":"8b9710227cce038554a2a8ebd42550c32d66e1e1","tid":1383671,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9d5264ba7178c6391380466bd6ef5f3c28320a","tid":1383671,"uid":221437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:19:12.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d4d1308915029f30b9c82006b7e3b83fc5104c","tid":1383671,"uid":173326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:23:55.000Z","msg":"除左之前嘅尋親活動繼續令班狗社交受打擊，仲要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">俾佢地班仔女以佢老豆老母為恥</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em>香港教育點失敗都唔會鼓吹暴力，班狗好多都有仔女讀緊中學、小學<br />\n</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">心理背景：<br />\n班黑警面對市民、其他公務員嘅唾罵都視若無睹、一錯在錯，原因有二：<br />\n1. 為左令屋企人有好生活、小朋友物質條件充裕，就算自己爛面，都要埋沒良心繼續攞份狗糧。<br />\n2. 街外人點睇唔理，反正自己生活圈子都係自己友圍爐，唔會覺得孤獨。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">行動：<br />\n<em><br />\n<ins>9月2號開學日，我地打工仔同大學生一齊請假一天</ins>，於各個間中、小學門口派發黑警濫用暴力嘅海報單張，尤其係對冇防具嘅市民都打/開槍（常見於連儂牆嗰啲）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為左真實呈現，要彩色印刷A4 size</span></span><br />\n<ins><em>派傳單唔係鼓勵遊行乜乜乜，而係傳達真相，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以唔犯法</span>。</em></span></em></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">攻效：<br />\n<ins>開學第一堂要教嘅字係個「警黑」字。</ins><br />\n如果小朋友/學生收到傳單，見到自己老豆老母嘅工作就係無差別打市民、向市民開槍，令到普通市民都無辜流血，一定好受打擊，返去問老豆老母點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">影響：<br />\n1. <ins>令黑警眾叛親離</ins>，連親生仔女都唾棄佢地，<ins>心理崩潰</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 令佢地<ins>小朋友心理受影響</ins>，令黑警要花多啲時間處理仔女情緒問題、修補關係，<ins>影響黑警於週末遊行嘅出勤率</ins>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 仔女為佢地黑警父母嘅惡行<ins>得到報應，警惕世人唔好為虎作倀、助紂為虐</ins>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<em>事前籌備：<br />\n1. 繼續整理過去6月至今嘅濫暴圖片，並持續收集嚟緊可能發生嘅濫暴素材。<br />\n2. 由於大量彩色列印需時，現時可以先行印刷已發生、fact checked嘅濫用暴力素材，下次發夢亦可以先行派發測試反應。</em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n認同請推post/討論<br />\n[跪求文宣急入] 攻心2.0 - 開學日去學校門口派黑警濫暴傳單<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380044</a>"},{"pid":"36e932586a7de65357816774e66eaf0643a4cbe9","tid":1383671,"uid":82067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:30:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">麻包袋</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b43653d0a0e4313b6a9d69b018d439f9925df08","tid":1383671,"uid":280234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:32:45.000Z","msg":"打副本啦大家"},{"pid":"da032b469610647a2803a4618933111d0abf835f","tid":1383671,"uid":274079,"like":